                     <interp inst="t17780715-58-off283" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17780715-58-off283" type="offenceSubcategory" value="theftFromPlace"></interp>
               stealing thirty-six linen shirts, value 5 l. eight pair of thread stockings, value 10 s. and two pair of black silk stocking breeches, value 20 s. the property of 
                     
                        <persName id="t17780715-58-victim548" type="victimName">
                           James
                            Brown
