                   in his dwelling-house
            </rs>. <rs id="t17780715-58-cd284" type="crimeDate">June 11th</rs>
                  <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17780715-58-off283 t17780715-58-cd284"></join>.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t17780715-58-person549">
                  CECILIA
                   BROWN
               <interp inst="t17780715-58-person549" type="surname" value="BROWN"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17780715-58-person549" type="given" value="CECILIA"></interp>
